title: fidget camp final showcase
description:
Final showcase for ​Fidget Camp! 

Fidget Camp is a week-long make-athon in San Francisco for creative exploration, featuring hands-on workshops (led by our campers!), community events, access to well-equipped workspace, and a final showcase of projects to the public.
